#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:coworking.welcome_article_body
msgid "if you need help!"
msgstr "以尋求協助！"

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:coworking.ir_ui_view_3303
msgid "info@yourcompany.example.com"
msgstr "info@yourcompany.example.com"

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:coworking.homepage
msgid "people sitting in front of computer monitors"
msgstr "人們坐着看電腦顯示器"

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:coworking.welcome_article_body
msgid "request a demo"
msgstr "預約功能演示"

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:coworking.ir_ui_view_4092
msgid "white and blue paper on pink surface"
msgstr "白色及藍色紙張，放在粉紅色平面上"

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:event.event,description:coworking.event_event_2
msgid ""
"☕ <strong>Quality Coffee &amp; Tea</strong> – Fuel for a productive day "
"ahead."
msgstr "☕ <strong>優質咖啡及茶</strong>：為你注入能量，助你高效工作一整天。"

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:event.event,description:coworking.event_event_3
msgid ""
"✍ <strong>Hands-On Exercises</strong> – Apply new methods immediately to "
"your work."
msgstr ""
"✍ <strong>動手實作練習</strong>：即時將新學到的方法，套用至實際工作上。"

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:event.event,description:coworking.event_event_1
msgid ""
"🍹 <strong>Drinks &amp; Snacks</strong> – A curated selection to keep the "
"conversation flowing."
msgstr "🍹 <strong>飲品及小食</strong>：精心挑選的提神茶點，讓你放懷暢談。"

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:event.event,description:coworking.event_event_2
msgid ""
"👋 <strong>Morning Networking</strong> – Meet fellow members before diving "
"into work."
msgstr ""
"👋 <strong>晨早交流時段</strong>：埋頭工作前，與其他使用者打招呼及交流。"

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:event.event,description:coworking.event_event_1
msgid ""
"💡 <strong>Inspiration</strong> – Exchange ideas in a relaxed, social "
"setting."
msgstr "💡 <strong>啟發靈感</strong>：享受輕鬆、友善的社交氣氛，隨意交流想法。"

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:event.event,description:coworking.event_event_3
msgid ""
"🤝 <strong>Collaborative Atmosphere</strong> – Connect with others who value "
"creativity and growth."
msgstr ""
"🤝 <strong>鼓勵協作的環境及氛圍</strong>：與其他重視創造力及業務增長的人，建"
"立商業聯繫。"

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:event.event,description:coworking.event_event_1
msgid ""
"🤝 <strong>Networking</strong> – Meet entrepreneurs, freelancers, and "
"creatives."
msgstr ""
"🤝 <strong>拓展人脈</strong>：認識創業人士、自由工作者、創意工作者等，彼此交"
"流。"

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:event.event,description:coworking.event_event_2
msgid ""
"🥯 <strong>Fresh Bagels</strong> – With a variety of toppings to suit every "
"taste."
msgstr "🥯 <strong>新鮮出爐比高包</strong>：多種配料選擇，滿足不同口味。"

#. module: coworking
#: model_terms:event.event,description:coworking.event_event_3
msgid ""
"🧠 <strong>Proven Strategies</strong> – Learn practical tools to stay "
"productive and inspired."
msgstr ""
"🧠 <strong>行之有效策略</strong>：學習如何運用不同實用工具，保持高效率工作，"
"並讓靈感源源不絕。"

